      "content": "For a truly sophisticated global professional, it's essential to adhere to timeless, culturally-agnostic standards that exude refinement and poise. A well-tailored, classic two-piece or three-piece suit in navy, charcoal, or black is a must, paired with crisp, white dress shirts and simple, elegant accessories. A well-groomed, neutral-colored haircut and subtle, high-quality jewelry, such as a simple watch and a classic wedding band, will complete the look. It's also crucial to master the art of subtle, nuanced body language, such as maintaining eye contact and using open, confident gestures.",
